{"tid":474194,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人唔興食牛？！","createTime":"2017-11-20T02:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T00:32:41.000Z","uid":139763,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"fb647849d336ebec049a8fd0f6f606339478b7cd","tid":474194,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T02:54:52.000Z","msg":"去親酒樓食飯<br />\n乳豬 炸子雞 蝦 魚都有<br />\n就係無牛<br />\n明明牛咁common<br />\n你話無羊都接受到<br />\n唔通中國人唔興食牛？？<br />\n定因為啲牛幫手耕田所以唔劏佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b3a211e54a4d21792109536a52ae3b422e6925","tid":474194,"uid":130657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"成本高"},{"pid":"0fc6e69da4ef8d66895075b468305099d0a27b49","tid":474194,"uid":154214,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去親酒樓食飯<br />\n乳豬 炸子雞 蝦 魚都有<br />\n就係無牛<br />\n明明牛咁common<br />\n你話無羊都接受到<br />\n唔通中國人唔興食牛？？<br />\n定因為啲牛幫手耕田所以唔劏佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛用來幫手耕田 而且大得比較慢<br />\n再加上一胎生得好少<br />\n所以多數應該養豬同食豬多"},{"pid":"4e4de3ff300275e374120cf42aec126e2c3d087a","tid":474194,"uid":146092,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"佢地食開屎"},{"pid":"cbd4df10bd9a8363b19722232d8eed6a05e81398","tid":474194,"uid":4917,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"班支那人呢，香港嘅滑雞，佢地唔啱食<br />\n要食佢支那走地嗰D，硬過你條命嘅雞"},{"pid":"22dd7fa40cdedef4159126183bfe4dd38acb7481","tid":474194,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:20:30.000Z","msg":"黑椒牛仔骨？薯仔牛柳粒 （甜甜地個隻)？"},{"pid":"72372d863ac0e09c6f6bfe6396084caa56b29f06","tid":474194,"uid":40272,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班支那人呢，香港嘅滑雞，佢地唔啱食<br />\n要食佢支那走地嗰D，硬過你條命嘅雞</blockquote><br />\n係咪你唔識食咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走地雞有雞咪仲要啲肉夠實<br />\n<br />\n著通個啲雞無味仲要啲肉係霉"},{"pid":"611d51da84e81801d852cac4d59814fea90e245b","tid":474194,"uid":146092,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班支那人呢，香港嘅滑雞，佢地唔啱食<br />\n要食佢支那走地嗰D，硬過你條命嘅雞</blockquote><br />\n係咪你唔識食咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走地雞有雞咪仲要啲肉夠實<br />\n<br />\n著通個啲雞無味仲要啲肉係霉</blockquote><br />\n啲小學雞一出世就食雪雞係咁架啦，食飯都唔夠力"},{"pid":"0c171f3f3f1ef319a539cb8087c6ab79213b1bd7","tid":474194,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑椒牛仔骨？薯仔牛柳粒 （甜甜地個隻)？</blockquote><br />\n我意思唔係小菜 係成圍嗰啲"},{"pid":"02f4e126137fa0f9e896b847c544fb378f2f5494","tid":474194,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"中國冇靚牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844403968e65f9c91b44e1dd70b25f64d2bf9e53","tid":474194,"uid":48277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"因為分不到"},{"pid":"c9aad52de7ca0022d3eb1df7e3f0d5b30d556a4f","tid":474194,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:50:54.000Z","msg":"中國d牛食垃圾大<br />\n雖然係好慘 但牛真係好有靈性<br />\n見到一車車..."},{"pid":"3e379dbd18ab19f3eb96ff2f02ac85eed80335ed","tid":474194,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"牛貴"},{"pid":"f406fabbd0c46a4ed3a88d94e4ef15f33bbaf248","tid":474194,"uid":48426,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班支那人呢，香港嘅滑雞，佢地唔啱食<br />\n要食佢支那走地嗰D，硬過你條命嘅雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食過走地雞未 <br />\n香港啲雞真係無雞味"},{"pid":"76678d4e60875df07e03ae9d51701bf0f7806b87","tid":474194,"uid":48796,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"古時拎嚟耕田<br />\n中醫話毒<br />\n信觀音同道教又戒牛<br />\n係會冇咁受歡迎"},{"pid":"78de91cbaf8fd0c3a5c0b6cb15ef126e7acfa1fd","tid":474194,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"因為大家都開始戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd443afc3211e10a86f327cbedae692d88a047d8","tid":474194,"uid":21412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"食開屎"},{"pid":"27bb2ec27374d1a41f3adcad1dd459b25e4d5eea","tid":474194,"uid":153566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班支那人呢，香港嘅滑雞，佢地唔啱食<br />\n要食佢支那走地嗰D，硬過你條命嘅雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食過走地雞未 <br />\n香港啲雞真係無雞味</blockquote><br />\n但係我覺得嘉美雞幾好食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf929532e4125231b6e78cd3b54fd4f305d3308","tid":474194,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"牛肉貴。同埋粵菜唔興用牛入饌。"},{"pid":"e3226bbab51c198349fef32d0107050b53661bd0","tid":474194,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班支那人呢，香港嘅滑雞，佢地唔啱食<br />\n要食佢支那走地嗰D，硬過你條命嘅雞</blockquote><br />\n煮法嚟講,的確香港好d<br />\n不過講雞味真係走地雞好d<br />\n所以最好係走地雞+香港煮法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,大陸用咩餵雞真係唔知,唔敢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e177e130bce3e920a9a1450623ef0ec89c40a2bc","tid":474194,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班支那人呢，香港嘅滑雞，佢地唔啱食<br />\n要食佢支那走地嗰D，硬過你條命嘅雞</blockquote><br />\n煮法嚟講,的確香港好d<br />\n不過講雞味真係走地雞好d<br />\n所以最好係走地雞+香港煮法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,大陸用咩餵雞真係唔知,唔敢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸啲「扇」雞正啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肥美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50dbaa05ea9b4093b36c5c97d2b40bc7a63ca90","tid":474194,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:04:43.000Z","msg":"老豆同阿伯差唔多高大<br />\n我老母仲高過伯母<br />\n<br />\n但加拿大長大既堂大佬 大隻過我勁多<br />\n<br />\n根據我父母既解釋就係佢成日食牛肉"},{"pid":"b3292947f7eee052d646d1433947df06a55d3852","tid":474194,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"酒席煮牛太過麻煩<br />\n生又出血唔老黎, 熟晒又唔好食"},{"pid":"cd5ca7f5ad39511cc746296f47f5dabc558489ed","tid":474194,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"因為牛牛聲唔好聽<br />\n所以多數婚宴冇牛"},{"pid":"b28eb8cbea136543f3722bd24cd4e9ea7e9abd08","tid":474194,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"興食狗"}]}